Man who fatally stabbed former co-worker during 1992 burglary has been executed in South Dakota
05 Nov 2019, 02:11 by EndPlay
SIOUX FALLS, S.D. - SIOUX FALLS, S.D. (AP) - Man who fatally stabbed former co-worker during 1992 burglary has been executed in South Dakota.
